#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn28.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn28.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 28 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 28 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Sāriputtavagga "
msgstr "1. With Sāriputta "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 9. Nirodhasamāpattisutta → nirodha (pts1)
msgctxt "sn28.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Nirodhasamāpattisutta "
msgstr "9. The Attainment of Cessation "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn28.9:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.9:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto … pe …. "
msgstr "Venerable Ānanda saw Venerable Sāriputta … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.9:1.3"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharāmi. "
msgstr "“Reverend, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, I entered and remained in the cessation of perception and feeling. "

msgctxt "sn28.9:1.4"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "But it didn’t occur to me: "

msgctxt "sn28.9:1.5"
msgid "‘ahaṃ saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpanno’ti vā ‘ahaṃ saññāvedayitanirodhā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti. "
msgstr "‘I am entering the cessation of perception and feeling’ or ‘I have entered the cessation of perception and feeling’ or ‘I am emerging from the cessation of perception and feeling’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.9:1.6"
msgid "Tathā hi panāyasmato sāriputtassa dīgharattaṃ ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānānusayā susamūhatā. "
msgstr "“That must be because Venerable Sāriputta has long ago totally eradicated ego, possessiveness, and the underlying tendency to conceit. "

msgctxt "sn28.9:1.7"
msgid "Tasmā āyasmato sāriputtassa na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "That’s why it didn’t occur to you: "

msgctxt "sn28.9:1.8"
msgid "“‘ahaṃ saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpanno’ti vā ‘ahaṃ saññāvedayitanirodhā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti. "
msgstr "‘I am entering the cessation of perception and feeling’ or ‘I have entered the cessation of perception and feeling’ or ‘I am emerging from the cessation of perception and feeling’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn28.9:1.9"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

